Installation Guide:

1.Turn Off Your Antimalware or Antvirus Before using the keygen.
2.Unpack and install the program (Do not insert any key when asked during the install!)
3.Run the program and choose "register" when registration screen pops up.
4.You can insert anything for Name & Company. Generate serial from the keygen and paste it into that box.
5.In the next screen choose "Other Options" (Important!)
6.Copy your "MAC ID" to the keymaker (right into installation ID section) and click on "Activation"
7.Copy that Activation code into the activation screen and choose "activate now". It's all done!

Note: Every computer has a different MAC ID, it must be copied into "Installation ID" part in the keygen, for activation code, obviously
